org.sql: SELECT projects.* FROM projects WHERE projects.status = 1 AND (SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.project_id = projects.id AND em.name = 'time_tracking') IS NOT NULL

rewrites.sql: SELECT projects.* FROM projects WHERE projects.status = 1 AND (SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.project_id = projects.id AND em.name = 'time_tracking' LIMIT 1) IS NOT NULL
